en:
The Ace Hotel Caen Nord Mémorial is ideally located near a green and relaxing setting, close to the Caen Memorial and the Colline aux Oiseaux floral park, a 10-minute drive from downtown Caen.

Accessible thanks to the N 814, a circular road around Caen, the Ace Hotel Caen Nord Mémorial will be an ideal stopover for visiting the Normandy area as well as for your business trips.

The measures put in place for the customers
- We are committed to respecting the directives and recommendations of the public authorities in force regarding the fight against COVID-19.
- Our objective is to make your stay pleasant by respecting the new sanitary measures.
